1
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,729
There are still a few days left.

2
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,080
I forgot my lines.

3
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:06,600
You didn't forfeit

4
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:08,180
just to let me win, did you?

5
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:12,810
Little girl,

6
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:15,000
are you playing Zixia with him?

7
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:17,840
No.

8
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:20,240
Well, yes.

9
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:22,000
She's shy.

10
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,560
I'll come back in a few days to rent more costumes.

11
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,920
Do you have the costumes for all the characters

12
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:28,320
in 'A Chinese Odyssey'?

13
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:28,920
Yes, we do.

14
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,400
Only my shop has them all.

15
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,600
Come with him next time, okay?

16
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:35,600
Okay.

17
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,880
I didn't expect you to come to a place like this.

18
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,320
We've competed in physics

19
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,320
and basketball.

20
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:58,800
Today, I want to see how good your billiards is.

21
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:01,460
You didn't ask me here just to play pool, did you?

22
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:03,160
What exactly do you want?

23
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:06,640
Quitting the drama competition doesn't seem like your style.

24
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,560
Can you tell me

25
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,400
why exactly?

26
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:12,160
I always do things based on my mood.

27
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,080
Is it any of your business?

28
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,280
Why so impatient?

29
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,240
Let's chat while we play.

30
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:19,579
I have nothing to chat with you about.

31
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:22,520
You rented Yuanbao's costume, didn't you?

32
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,520
I thought you didn't want her to win.

33
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,840
Why did you help her?

34
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,290
Does it concern you?

35
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,040
Mu Qingjun.

36
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,720
I've never met a rival growing up,

37
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,400
whether in studies

38
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:38,200
or anything else.

39
00:03:38,640 --> 00:03:40,640
But you are an exception.

40
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:43,360
You are indeed very capable.

41
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:46,120
But I hate it most when people yield like it's charity.

42
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,520
You obviously didn't cheat on the physics exam.

43
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,980
Yet you said you copied me.

44
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:50,920
For this drama festival,

45
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:53,250
I was planning to compete with you fairly.

46
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:55,800
I didn't expect you to drop out halfway.

47
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,720
This feeling

48
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,940
makes me very uncomfortable.

49
00:03:59,000 --> 00:03:59,640
Is that so?

50
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,440
Seeing you uncomfortable

51
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,920
makes me feel pretty good.

52
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:07,840
I know deep down

53
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,860
you want to perform with Yuanbao.

54
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:10,940
How about this?

55
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,850
Let's have a fair competition.

56
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:15,480
If you win, you play Joker,

57
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,800
and I'll quit. How about it?

58
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,600
Meng Jingu, you better act well.

59
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,380
Didn't you want to act?

60
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:15,480
What I want is not important.

61
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:18,880
What's important is that Yuanbao wants to act with you.

62
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,560
So you better not let her down.

63
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:22,680
Otherwise I won't spare you.

64
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:25,840
Also,

65
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:29,320
Yuanbao really wants to make friends with you.

66
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,320
If you are not sincere,

67
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:34,880
I will make it impossible for you to stay in Zhicheng.

68
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:35,920
I mean what I say.

69
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:48,880
150.

70
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,880
170.

71
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,520
170.

72
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:58,000
170.

73
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,800
200.

74
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,880
203.

75
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,840
Why is it so little?

76
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:14,320
Actually, as long as Mutou is here,

77
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,560
I feel at ease for some reason.

78
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:19,050
When we performed in class before,

79
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,810
it was always just the two of us.

80
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:23,640
Leaving him behind and choosing Meng Jingu this time,

81
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:25,280
he must be feeling upset.

82
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:28,480
No, Mutou has been sensitive since childhood.

83
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:31,580
I still need to save up for a nice gift to cheer him up.

84
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,250
Little pig, little pig.

85
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:40,360
You have to grow up fast.

86
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:46,840
Brother Mutou, thank you for renting the clothes.

87
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,720
Please allow me to treat you

88
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:51,520
to ice cream another day as a token of my gratitude.

89
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,760
I want two.

90
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:22,260
All three are fine. Just don't get an upset stomach.

91
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:31,340
Yuanbao really wants to be friends with you.

92
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,920
I'm going to study now.

93
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,840
Come on, Yuanbao.

94
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,040
Yuanbao.

95
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:04,050
You're actually quite excellent.

96
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:06,680
What?

97
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:07,880
Nothing.

98
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,610
I just wanted to say,

99
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:12,080
don't forget to rehearse after school.

100
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:14,440
The competition is coming up. We need to hurry.

101
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:15,200
Don't worry.

102
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:18,080
I've memorized it thoroughly these past few days.

103
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:26,400
Aren't you Zhizunbao and Zixia?

104
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,520
Who are you picking clothes for today?

105
00:08:28,520 --> 00:08:30,440
Well, I'm not acting anymore.

106
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,640
I brought my classmates to pick out some clothes.

107
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:34,640
All right. What clothes do you need?

108
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:37,600
We also need costumes for the other characters.

109
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,760
The clothes are upstairs.

110
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:40,400
Let them all come in, okay?

111
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:41,559
Come.

112
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,860
They're all on the second floor. Take your pick.

113
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,290
This one is good.

114
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:53,180
There's a Zhu Bajie mask here.

115
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,440
So many clothes!

116
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:59,120
So annoying.

117
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,000
What is this?

118
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:05,680
You didn't keep your pig in its pen, did you?

119
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,480
Ruirui.

120
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,520
This is Princess Iron Fan.

121
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:14,840
Qingyun.

122
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,320
Look, Zhu Bajie's mask.

123
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:18,360
Didn't you say you didn't like Zhu Bajie yesterday?

124
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,960
Why are you so excited today?

125
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,770
I like him today.

126
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:22,520
Look,

127
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:24,560
here are the Fifth Prince's clothes.

128
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:25,520
My Guanyin.

129
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:26,800
How is it?

130
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,440
Can I act in a Qing Dynasty drama

131
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:30,240
if I wear this?

132
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:32,900
Then you'll have to shave your head bald.

133
00:09:32,920 --> 00:09:33,760
Get lost.

134
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:38,280
Did I eat too much today?

135
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,960
I hope it fits.

136
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:42,680
It'll fit. I'm looking forward to it.

137
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:47,360
Ruirui, let's go.

138
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:48,320
Go.

139
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:51,200
Selling pigs.

140
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:53,200
Cheap.

141
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,280
Your pig

142
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:56,080
looks like it's pregnant with seven piglets.

143
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:58,040
Guaranteed profit.

144
00:09:59,160 --> 00:09:59,920
Sloppy pig.

145
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,640
Does it look good, Mutou?

146
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,660
It's quite pretty.

147
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,100
Looks good.

148
00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:36,330
Yours looks quite good too.

149
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:37,360
Thank you.

150
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:50,840
Try harder next time. You are still Zhi Zun Bao.

151
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:51,560
Come on.

152
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:01,540
Yaqi, you'd definitely look much better in it than her.

153
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:02,440
No.

154
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:04,650
I think Yuanbao looks quite good in it.

155
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:07,250
What's so good about it?

156
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:09,600
Yuanbao.

157
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:11,810
You finally look like a girl today.

158
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:13,560
You...

159
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,360
Well...

160
00:11:16,560 --> 00:11:17,960
Let's take a costume photo together.

161
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:18,760
Okay.

162
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:19,920
Come on.

163
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,080
Let's go.

164
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:22,840
Come on.

165
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:25,480
Wait a minute.

166
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,160
What are you doing?

167
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:29,960
Come, let's take a photo together.

168
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:30,800
Come on.

169
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,860
Come, I'll count three, two, one.

170
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:34,800
Let's take a picture together.

171
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:35,960
Say cheese.

172
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:40,400
Three, two, one, cheese!

173
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:44,880
All right.

174
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:45,680
All right, all right.

175
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:46,480
Got it, got it.

176
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:48,280
Everyone, please make sure to put away your costumes

177
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:49,880
and props carefully.

178
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:50,880
When we get to the school,

179
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:53,340
they will be managed by Qiao Yan and Qingyun.

180
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:39,760
Stand up.

181
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:43,760
Hello, teacher.

182
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,890
Hello, students. Please sit down.

183
00:12:46,560 --> 00:12:47,690
We have a new student

184
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:49,480
transferring to our class today.

185
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,080
Get along well with each other.

186
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:52,000
Such a big event,

187
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:53,440
and I didn't hear a word about it.

188
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,440
That makes no sense.

189
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:55,560
Yeah, really.

190
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:56,680
Come in.

191
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:23,120
She is so pretty!

192
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:25,480
Please introduce yourself.

193
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:27,520
Hello everyone, my name is Gu Xinrui.

194
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:29,120
Please take care of me.

195
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:32,960
Come on, let's give her a round of applause.

196
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,280
Welcome.

197
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,720
Xinrui, go to the last row

198
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:39,360
and sit with Mu Qingjun.

199
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,000
Okay.

200
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,200
Mu Qingjun.

201
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,000
Don't distract the new student in class.

202
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:46,720
Got it.

203
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:55,040
So beautiful.

204
00:13:58,680 --> 00:13:59,440
Hello.

205
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:00,450
World Military.

206
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:06,160
All right.

207
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:08,460
Everyone, open yesterday's exam paper.

208
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:10,840
You have 20 minutes to do it.

209
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:12,320
Then we'll go over it.

210
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:14,520
Where did this girl transfer from?

211
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:15,840
She is so pretty.

212
00:14:16,400 --> 00:14:17,640
Don't you think

213
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:20,560
she outshines Xing Yaqi?

214
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,280
Pretty much.

215
00:14:22,560 --> 00:14:23,680
What are you talking about?

216
00:14:23,680 --> 00:14:25,280
She's a typical rich beauty.

217
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:27,320
Shang Ningyu.

218
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:29,380
You know this goddess?

219
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,920
We were middle school classmates.

220
00:14:30,920 --> 00:14:32,320
She was the school belle.

221
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:33,700
Who is talking?

222
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:40,480
Goodbye, teacher.

223
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:41,640
Goodbye, class.

224
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,640
Xinrui, why are you here?

225
00:14:44,880 --> 00:14:45,810
You are here too?

226
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:46,520
Did you just transfer here?

227
00:14:46,520 --> 00:14:47,650
You know each other?

228
00:14:48,640 --> 00:14:49,800
Middle school classmates.

229
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:52,400
Weren't you in some... some...

230
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:52,920
The UK?

231
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:53,960
Yes, yes, yes.

232
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:56,360
Yes, I just came back a few days ago.

233
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,160
That's great.

234
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,720
I'm just still not quite used to it.

235
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:00,920
Come outside with me.

236
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:02,840
Okay.

237
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,640
Why did he ask her to go outside?

238
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:08,500
They seem to know each other well.

239
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:10,600
She went right out when he called.

240
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:11,800
Hurry, hurry, hurry.

241
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,620
What? What's going on?

242
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:18,160
Yuanbao.

243
00:15:21,640 --> 00:15:23,400
I've been looking for you for a while.

244
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:24,920
Why did you come here alone?

245
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:26,380
Why didn't you wait for me?

246
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:30,480
I didn't want to interrupt your chat with the new classmate.

247
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:32,000
So I just...

248
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:32,840
Xinrui.

249
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:35,890
She's actually not just my classmate,

250
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:37,520
but also my sister.

251
00:15:38,640 --> 00:15:39,400
Your sister?

252
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:43,080
Our relationship is just like yours and Qingyun's.

253
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,920
We grew up together like siblings.

254
00:15:44,920 --> 00:15:46,250
She went abroad before.

255
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:49,800
But now she suddenly came back because of a back injury.

256
00:15:49,920 --> 00:15:50,960
She didn't even tell me.

257
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:52,420
I was quite surprised too.

258
00:15:54,640 --> 00:15:55,900
Don't misunderstand.

259
00:15:56,760 --> 00:15:58,160
It's fine. That's good.

260
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:07,600
What's wrong, bro?

261
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:09,280
Did I do something wrong?

262
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:10,000
No.

263
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:11,610
Let me buy you a cola.

264
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:12,920
Okay, thank you.

265
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:24,530
What happened at the cinema

266
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:26,240
that day?

267
00:16:26,920 --> 00:16:28,360
Did I misunderstand?

268
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:29,800
Could it be

269
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:33,280
that she didn't give me the movie ticket secretly?

270
00:16:33,520 --> 00:16:34,680
Should I ask her?

271
00:16:35,640 --> 00:16:36,640
If I ask,

272
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:38,890
it might be awkward.

273
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,240
Mr. Liu.

274
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:58,320
Why does he have that movie ticket?

275
00:16:59,040 --> 00:17:00,160
Should I ask him?

276
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:02,800
Forget it.

277
00:17:03,160 --> 00:17:05,220
I'll just pretend nothing happened.

278
00:17:06,839 --> 00:17:07,880
Um.

279
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:10,680
Um, you go first.

280
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:13,040
I'm fine, you go first.

281
00:17:13,960 --> 00:17:15,680
Um, I just wanted to say

282
00:17:16,200 --> 00:17:17,730
that our students recently

283
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:19,520
have been very motivated

284
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:20,930
to learn chemistry.

285
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:22,319
This is all to your credit.

286
00:17:22,319 --> 00:17:22,960
No.

287
00:17:23,280 --> 00:17:25,599
It's because you are a good homeroom teacher.

288
00:17:25,599 --> 00:17:26,240
No.

289
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:27,650
I can't take the credit.

290
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:28,920
They really like you.

291
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:30,600
They only like me because they like you.

292
00:17:30,600 --> 00:17:32,360
No, they like you.

293
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:33,160
They like you.

294
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:35,440
They like you.

295
00:17:38,440 --> 00:17:40,680
I have something else to do.

296
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:42,040
I'll get going now.

297
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:43,160
Um...

298
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:44,920
Mr. Xu.

299
00:17:49,360 --> 00:17:50,080
Mr. Tian.

300
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:53,040
Mu Qingyun, why didn't you knock again?

301
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:54,320
Alright.

302
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:55,800
What is it?

303
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:59,280
I want to play Zhi Zunbao.

304
00:17:59,280 --> 00:18:01,160
Mu Qingyun, the performance is starting soon.

305
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:02,680
Can you stop making trouble?

306
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,880
I'm not making trouble.

307
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:05,280
How is this not making trouble?

308
00:18:05,280 --> 00:18:06,280
You perform when you want to,

309
00:18:06,280 --> 00:18:07,680
and quit when you want to.

310
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:09,320
Do you think your family owns this school?

311
00:18:09,320 --> 00:18:11,280
You think you can do whatever you want?

312
00:18:11,280 --> 00:18:12,040
Mu Qingyun.

313
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:14,080
A real man

314
00:18:14,320 --> 00:18:16,040
always keeps his word.

315
00:18:16,320 --> 00:18:18,880
You have to be responsible for your own decisions and words.

316
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:19,720
Exactly.

317
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:23,960
This.

318
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:27,850
You are messing around.

319
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:31,320
Mr. Tian,

320
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:34,120
I think it's a good thing for students to be proactive.

321
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:35,120
Don't be angry.

322
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:36,040
Look at this child,

323
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:37,720
if they put this cleverness into their studies,

324
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:39,200
their grades would have improved long ago.

325
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,560
Well, I'll talk to

326
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:41,920
the class monitors again.

327
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:43,120
Go back.

328
00:18:43,520 --> 00:18:44,160
Okay.

329
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:47,760
Yuanbao, this time

330
00:18:47,840 --> 00:18:49,920
you're the highly anticipated female lead.

331
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:51,520
Because of your hard work,

332
00:18:51,640 --> 00:18:53,080
I am truly happy for you.

333
00:18:55,120 --> 00:18:57,560
But I'm naturally bad at art.

334
00:18:57,760 --> 00:19:00,040
However, I believe what my grandmother said.

335
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:01,280
Man can conquer nature.

336
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:03,480
We can rely on our hard work acquired

337
00:19:03,600 --> 00:19:04,840
to change our destiny.

338
00:19:04,840 --> 00:19:05,880
Let's work hard together.

339
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:06,560
Okay.

340
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:07,760
Cheer up!

341
00:19:07,960 --> 00:19:08,760
Cheer up!

342
00:19:08,800 --> 00:19:10,200
Hello, Yuanbao. Hello, Ruirui.

343
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:11,720
Let's have a drink together.

344
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:13,480
Thank you.

345
00:19:13,640 --> 00:19:14,570
You're welcome.

346
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:17,250
I heard you're going to act in a play together.

347
00:19:17,320 --> 00:19:18,640
That's great.

348
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:21,090
Looking forward to your performance.

349
00:19:22,480 --> 00:19:23,340
I just got here.

350
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:25,680
I'm not familiar with many people yet.

351
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:27,600
I heard from Jingu that you are sincere

352
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:28,920
and loyal to your friends.

353
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:29,640
So,

354
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:31,580
I hope to be good friends with you.

355
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:33,000
It's fine.

356
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:34,160
My desk mate's good friend

357
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:35,440
is my good friend.

358
00:19:35,720 --> 00:19:36,280
Really?

359
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:37,200
That's great.

360
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:38,840
From now on, we are good friends.

361
00:19:38,840 --> 00:19:39,360
Okay,

362
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:40,320
no problem.

363
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:44,290
It seems you don't have to take PE classes.

364
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:48,260
I used to be an art student and practice dancing.

365
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:49,920
But after a year abroad,

366
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:51,660
I injured my waist.

367
00:19:52,120 --> 00:19:52,920
In the future,

368
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:55,980
I might not be able to practice dancing anymore.

369
00:19:56,480 --> 00:19:57,320
Don't be discouraged.

370
00:19:57,320 --> 00:19:58,680
We will all support you.

371
00:19:59,160 --> 00:20:01,480
I still want to learn dancing with you then.

372
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:02,240
Okay,

373
00:20:02,440 --> 00:20:04,560
then I can teach you.

374
00:20:04,720 --> 00:20:05,080
Okay.

375
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:06,840
Okay, you can teach us then.

376
00:20:07,280 --> 00:20:09,440
I want to see how you dance that Xinjiang dance.

377
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:10,080
Together.

378
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:17,280
Qiao Yan.

379
00:20:18,440 --> 00:20:19,970
What's wrong with your arm?

380
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:20,640
Nothing.

381
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:21,720
Are you injured?

382
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:23,730
Yes, I accidentally bumped it.

383
00:20:25,040 --> 00:20:26,400
I always see you

384
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:27,760
covered in bruises.

385
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:29,000
Are you okay?

386
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:30,400
I'm fine.

387
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:32,850
I'll be more careful in the future.

388
00:20:33,080 --> 00:20:33,760
But Yaqi,

389
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:35,440
look at Xiong Yuanbao.

390
00:20:36,520 --> 00:20:39,200
Although she has poor grades and is unreliable,

391
00:20:39,760 --> 00:20:41,560
Mu Qingyun and Meng Jingu

392
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:43,640
are both very nice to her.

393
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,080
Don't say that.

394
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:46,320
She and Qingyun

395
00:20:46,360 --> 00:20:47,520
grew up together.

396
00:20:47,640 --> 00:20:49,440
Meng Jingu is also her desk mate,

397
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:51,920
so it's normal for them to have a good relationship.

398
00:20:51,920 --> 00:20:53,050
Don't overthink it.

399
00:20:53,560 --> 00:20:55,040
Then why do I feel

400
00:20:55,320 --> 00:20:57,560
the way you look at Mu Qingyun recently

401
00:20:57,720 --> 00:20:58,980
is a little different?

402
00:21:00,360 --> 00:21:01,200
No.

403
00:21:01,600 --> 00:21:02,400
No?

404
00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:04,020
Then why are you blushing?

405
00:21:05,040 --> 00:21:06,160
I'm not blushing.

406
00:21:07,360 --> 00:21:08,490
By the way, Qiao Yan.

407
00:21:08,560 --> 00:21:10,560
Why didn't you act in 'A Chinese Odyssey'?

408
00:21:10,560 --> 00:21:12,400
You served everyone the whole time.

409
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:13,530
That's not like you.

410
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:16,960
I just feel it would interfere with my studies.

411
00:21:16,960 --> 00:21:18,200
Besides, my dad doesn't like

412
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:21,400
me participating in activities unrelated to my studies.

413
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:23,010
All right, go ahead.

414
00:21:23,080 --> 00:21:24,440
Class is about to end. Let's go gather.

415
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:25,040
Let's go.

416
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:35,600
Brother, if you really have something on your mind,

417
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:37,240
why don't you tell me about it?

418
00:21:37,240 --> 00:21:39,040
Maybe I can give you some advice.

419
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:41,930
I want to strangle someone.

420
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:43,640
My dear brother!

421
00:21:43,800 --> 00:21:45,160
Take my advice.

422
00:21:45,560 --> 00:21:47,800
There are plenty of fish in the sea.

423
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:49,930
Why do you keep thinking about her?

424
00:21:50,320 --> 00:21:52,320
Maybe she just sees you as a brother.

425
00:21:52,320 --> 00:21:53,760
Are you overthinking it?

426
00:21:56,240 --> 00:21:58,040
What was the last thing you said?

427
00:21:58,240 --> 00:21:59,040
I said,

428
00:21:59,360 --> 00:22:01,080
she just sees you as a brother.

429
00:22:01,440 --> 00:22:03,880
Are you overthinking it?

430
00:22:04,120 --> 00:22:05,780
Yes, yes, yes. That's the one.

431
00:22:10,760 --> 00:22:12,160
Traveling through time,

432
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:14,320
we seem to see

433
00:22:14,600 --> 00:22:17,640
that young wet nurse in Jiaodong.

434
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:19,680
Close at hand,

435
00:22:20,120 --> 00:22:21,720
we deeply feel

436
00:22:21,760 --> 00:22:24,920
the burning heat of a mother's chest.

437
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:26,560
At Jiaodong Nursery,

438
00:22:26,840 --> 00:22:28,880
there is my childhood wet nurse.

439
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:31,000
More than 300 women from Rushan.

440
00:22:31,120 --> 00:22:33,980
I'm afraid I won't be able to see without my glasses.

441
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:37,160
I, Old Bull, will do it.

442
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:39,320
Why can't I remember the lines?

443
00:22:40,720 --> 00:22:41,520
Back then.

444
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:43,440
Help me tie this, Yuanbao.

445
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:44,080
Sure.

446
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:44,880
Let me see.

447
00:22:45,240 --> 00:22:47,280
There is a strap here in the back.

448
00:22:47,360 --> 00:22:48,690
You can make it tighter.

449
00:22:49,960 --> 00:22:50,440
All right.

450
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:51,120
Like this.

451
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:52,860
Is it too tight?

452
00:22:54,120 --> 00:22:55,650
I'll loosen it a bit for you.

453
00:22:57,840 --> 00:22:59,200
I'm holding my breath.

454
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:01,000
Tong Ruirui, suck your stomach in.

455
00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:02,000
Who to choose?

456
00:23:02,240 --> 00:23:03,240
Who to choose?

457
00:23:03,520 --> 00:23:03,960
Is this okay?

458
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:06,220
She has always just seen you as a brother.

459
00:23:06,280 --> 00:23:08,000
Are you overthinking it?

460
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:10,120
I'll redo it for you.

461
00:23:10,120 --> 00:23:12,040
The next group is Class 20, Grade 1.

462
00:23:12,040 --> 00:23:14,100
Please get ready for your rehearsal.

463
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:20,920
How is it?

464
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:22,680
What's wrong?

465
00:23:23,360 --> 00:23:24,560
It's almost our class's turn.

466
00:23:24,560 --> 00:23:26,220
But Meng Jingu isn't here yet.

467
00:23:26,360 --> 00:23:27,520
What should we do?

468
00:23:27,960 --> 00:23:28,920
Call him again.

469
00:23:37,320 --> 00:23:38,360
He's not answering.

470
00:23:38,360 --> 00:23:40,890
Could something have happened to Meng Jingu?

471
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:42,360
I don't think so.

472
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:44,600
Did you tell Mr. Tian?

473
00:23:45,240 --> 00:23:47,520
Mr. Tian is in a meeting and can't be reached.

474
00:23:47,520 --> 00:23:49,000
Could he have given up?

475
00:23:49,120 --> 00:23:50,040
No.

476
00:23:52,080 --> 00:23:54,120
Meng Jingu isn't that kind of person.

477
00:23:54,120 --> 00:23:55,880
Why don't we talk to the host

478
00:23:56,040 --> 00:23:57,080
and ask them to push

479
00:23:57,080 --> 00:23:58,480
our rehearsal slot back?

480
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:00,490
We have no other choice.

481
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:02,210
I'll go talk to them.

482
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:12,040
Hello, excuse me.

483
00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:14,260
We are missing a student in our class.

484
00:24:14,280 --> 00:24:16,400
How about this? You guys rehearse first.

485
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:17,000
All right.

486
00:24:20,280 --> 00:24:22,540
They should be here in about ten minutes.

487
00:24:25,120 --> 00:24:25,640
Gulai,

488
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:26,480
Jin Gulai.

489
00:24:26,760 --> 00:24:29,090
Pour tea for your Uncle Qin and Sister Qin.

490
00:24:29,320 --> 00:24:31,160
Your Sister Qin took time out

491
00:24:31,200 --> 00:24:33,480
of her busy schedule to bring you study notes.

492
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:35,740
Sharing learning experiences with you.

493
00:24:35,760 --> 00:24:37,290
That is really a rare thing.

494
00:24:38,600 --> 00:24:40,060
Thanks for your hard work.

495
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:42,720
Give me my phone back.

496
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:43,800
I really...

497
00:24:44,760 --> 00:24:45,800
Come, have some tea.

498
00:24:45,800 --> 00:24:46,440
Okay.

499
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:47,280
Have some tea.

500
00:24:48,320 --> 00:24:50,600
Uncle, Jingu really has something to do today.

501
00:24:50,600 --> 00:24:51,600
How about...

502
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:56,480
I'm sorry.

503
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:58,080
Mr. Qin, Ms. Qin,

504
00:24:58,280 --> 00:25:00,280
I have something really important today.

505
00:25:00,280 --> 00:25:01,340
I must go right now.

506
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:03,440
Please excuse me.

507
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:05,200
Stop right there.

508
00:25:06,080 --> 00:25:07,540
Is some silly performance

509
00:25:07,800 --> 00:25:10,330
more important than your future and studies?

510
00:25:13,160 --> 00:25:15,320
You have already rescheduled the rehearsal four times.

511
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:17,250
Now we've put you in the last group.

512
00:25:17,280 --> 00:25:18,760
Is your teammate still not here?

513
00:25:18,760 --> 00:25:20,880
He'll be here soon.

514
00:25:21,080 --> 00:25:22,680
Please wait a little longer.

515
00:25:24,120 --> 00:25:26,000
We really don't have that much time.

516
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:27,800
Besides, we have to clean up.

517
00:25:28,280 --> 00:25:30,200
The competition will officially start tonight.

518
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:32,000
We can wait for ten more minutes at most.

519
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:33,120
If he still doesn't show up,

520
00:25:33,120 --> 00:25:34,880
you will have to miss the rehearsal.

521
00:25:34,880 --> 00:25:37,120
Whether you can perform depends on the teacher.

522
00:25:37,120 --> 00:25:39,520
Meng Jingu shouldn't be so unreliable.

523
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:41,240
Why isn't he here yet?

524
00:25:41,440 --> 00:25:42,880
I did some reckoning,

525
00:25:43,080 --> 00:25:44,080
this matter

526
00:25:44,320 --> 00:25:45,280
is very ominous.

527
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:48,250
Shut your jinxed mouth.

528
00:25:49,760 --> 00:25:51,360
Is Meng Jingu still not here?

529
00:25:52,360 --> 00:25:54,840
Meng Jingu standing us up without a word

530
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:56,560
is not his style.

531
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:58,080
What's going on?

532
00:25:58,480 --> 00:26:00,800
The rehearsal is to coordinate with the lights and music.

533
00:26:00,800 --> 00:26:02,000
Since he is not here,

534
00:26:02,800 --> 00:26:05,040
how about this? You guys go on stage first,

535
00:26:05,040 --> 00:26:06,560
and leave his lines empty.

536
00:26:06,720 --> 00:26:08,520
We can't miss this opportunity.

537
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:11,800
But Yuanbao and Meng Jingu

538
00:26:11,800 --> 00:26:13,240
have so many scenes together.

539
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:14,480
If Meng Jingu doesn't come,

540
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,720
we can't let Yuanbao

541
00:26:15,760 --> 00:26:17,090
put on a one-woman show.

542
00:26:17,360 --> 00:26:18,800
Right, Yuanbao can't

543
00:26:18,840 --> 00:26:20,400
just act into thin air.

544
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:22,080
No one is here to read lines with her.

545
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:25,140
She won't even know if she's acting too fast or too slow.

546
00:26:28,360 --> 00:26:30,200
Let's not wait anymore. Let's rehearse.

547
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:31,360
We can't miss this opportunity

548
00:26:31,360 --> 00:26:32,440
because of him.

549
00:26:33,240 --> 00:26:34,840
I will try my best to act well.

550
00:26:35,160 --> 00:26:36,360
Let's all do our best.

551
00:26:36,880 --> 00:26:37,810
I'll try my best.

552
00:26:38,800 --> 00:26:40,600
Let's go.

553
00:26:40,680 --> 00:26:41,240
Let's go.

554
00:26:41,680 --> 00:26:42,680
Come on, Yuanbao.

555
00:26:46,080 --> 00:26:48,480
What are you doing? Are you trying to rebel?

556
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:50,280
Dad, I'm really going to be late.

557
00:26:50,280 --> 00:26:52,040
I'm begging you, let me go.

558
00:26:52,600 --> 00:26:54,260
I wanted you to study finance,

559
00:26:54,560 --> 00:26:56,960
but you stubbornly insisted on studying physics.

560
00:26:56,960 --> 00:26:58,600
Fine, I let you have your way.

561
00:26:59,080 --> 00:27:00,280
I let you have your way because

562
00:27:00,280 --> 00:27:02,120
you actually had some ideas of your own.

563
00:27:02,120 --> 00:27:03,280
But now I realize

564
00:27:03,560 --> 00:27:05,220
that I've really spoiled you.

565
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:08,280
You can't even get your priorities straight.

566
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:09,920
Instead of studying,

567
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:12,200
you hang out with those poor students all day,

568
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,680
doing useless things.

569
00:27:14,560 --> 00:27:15,360
Today, you made me

570
00:27:15,360 --> 00:27:17,160
lose face in front of outsiders.

571
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:19,960
You don't even have any manners.

572
00:27:20,080 --> 00:27:21,520
You're going too far.

573
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:25,720
Jingu, your dad has a bad heart.

574
00:27:25,840 --> 00:27:27,480
He's just doing this for your own good.

575
00:27:27,480 --> 00:27:29,440
Uncle Qin and Sister Qin came today.

576
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:31,370
How could you just leave like that?

577
00:27:32,640 --> 00:27:33,920
I am not your puppet.

578
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:36,500
I have my own thoughts.

579
00:27:36,800 --> 00:27:38,460
I have my own life and friends.

580
00:27:38,680 --> 00:27:40,240
Can you please respect me?

581
00:27:40,760 --> 00:27:42,480
We don't respect you?

582
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:45,200
I think you don't realize how lucky you are.

583
00:27:45,280 --> 00:27:47,240
You will stay in your room today.

584
00:27:47,560 --> 00:27:48,880
When you figure things out,

585
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:50,080
then you can come out.

586
00:27:59,320 --> 00:28:01,680
Xinrui, please talk some sense into Jingu.

587
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:04,000
He won't listen to us right now.

588
00:28:13,960 --> 00:28:14,800
Jingu.

589
00:28:15,600 --> 00:28:18,080
No matter what, Uncle Meng has his reasons.

590
00:28:18,560 --> 00:28:20,820
They must be doing this for your own good.

591
00:28:21,040 --> 00:28:22,700
That's what he thinks is good.

592
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:26,360
The root of the problem is that he is too dictatorial.

593
00:28:26,360 --> 00:28:28,360
But even if you rush there now,

594
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:29,800
I'm afraid it's too late.

595
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:31,280
How about

596
00:28:31,800 --> 00:28:32,730
we just let it go?

597
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:34,440
No.

598
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:36,660
They are still waiting for me.

599
00:28:36,840 --> 00:28:37,480
Xinrui.

600
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:38,400
Can you

601
00:28:38,400 --> 00:28:39,800
call Yuanbao for me

602
00:28:40,280 --> 00:28:42,080
and explain my situation to her?

603
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:45,720
But I don't have our classmates' contact info,

604
00:28:45,840 --> 00:28:47,770
and Uncle confiscated your phone.

605
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:49,780
How am I supposed to contact them?

606
00:28:50,440 --> 00:28:51,840
Then can you go see her?

607
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:54,280
Explain my situation to her.

608
00:28:55,040 --> 00:28:55,840
Okay?

609
00:29:01,560 --> 00:29:02,160
Xinrui.

610
00:29:03,240 --> 00:29:03,920
Okay.

611
00:29:05,040 --> 00:29:07,320
I'll go explain it for you.

612
00:29:17,320 --> 00:29:19,080
You insolent monkey.

613
00:29:19,640 --> 00:29:22,200
To marry the Bull Demon King's sister,

614
00:29:22,400 --> 00:29:25,440
you actually offered your master Tang Sanzang as a wedding gift.

615
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:28,440
You even invited demons and monsters to eat his flesh.

616
00:29:28,560 --> 00:29:30,320
Do you admit your mistake?

617
00:29:30,440 --> 00:29:33,440
You crazy woman! You've chased me for three days and three nights.

618
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:36,040
If you weren't a woman, I would have killed you.

619
00:29:36,080 --> 00:29:37,610
You think I'm afraid of you?

620
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:51,640
Wukong,

621
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:53,560
how many times have I told you?

622
00:29:53,720 --> 00:29:56,120
Don't throw things around.

623
00:29:56,320 --> 00:29:58,880
What if it hits a kid?

624
00:29:59,040 --> 00:30:00,680
Even if it doesn't hit a kid,

625
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:02,180
it could hit some flowers.

626
00:30:02,880 --> 00:30:04,680
You seem to have hit me too early.

627
00:30:06,280 --> 00:30:07,280
What should we do?

628
00:30:07,520 --> 00:30:09,050
Never mind. I'll just fall.

629
00:30:10,120 --> 00:30:11,160
It hurts.

630
00:30:11,520 --> 00:30:12,480
Help me up.

631
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:23,600
Hurry up.

632
00:30:25,720 --> 00:30:26,600
It's starting.

633
00:30:28,080 --> 00:30:30,360
Today is the wedding day of my brother

634
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:33,040
and my sister Xiangxiang.

635
00:30:33,520 --> 00:30:34,520
Next, I announce

636
00:30:34,800 --> 00:30:38,800
that I will also marry Fairy Zixia.

637
00:30:40,320 --> 00:30:41,250
What did you say?

638
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:44,090
You are going to marry Fairy Zixia?

639
00:30:44,320 --> 00:30:45,160
My wife.

640
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:49,320
Are you planning to keep a mistress?

641
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:50,880
How could I, my wife?

642
00:30:51,040 --> 00:30:52,800
It's a rumor.

643
00:30:53,440 --> 00:30:54,720
Like hell I'll believe you.

644
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:55,600
Take this.

645
00:30:56,760 --> 00:30:58,720
I'm sorry, my wife.

646
00:31:00,280 --> 00:31:01,680
Still can't get through?

647
00:31:03,360 --> 00:31:04,290
What should I do?

648
00:31:11,040 --> 00:31:11,680
Come on.

649
00:31:12,160 --> 00:31:13,200
Come on, Xiong.

650
00:31:13,320 --> 00:31:15,240
Come on, Yuanbao.

651
00:31:30,280 --> 00:31:32,760
Joker, you bastard.

652
00:31:33,040 --> 00:31:34,080
Come out here!

653
00:31:46,800 --> 00:31:47,440
Yuanbao.

654
00:31:48,080 --> 00:31:49,000
Keep acting.

655
00:31:49,080 --> 00:31:49,960
Keep acting.

656
00:31:50,040 --> 00:31:50,760
Come on.

657
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:52,000
I am here.
